		<RichText x="738" y="255" width="439" height="85" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">凛狼对玩家进行至多抓，咬，咬3段攻击，依次造成<span color="#99ffff">50%,40%,70%</span><span>伤害，可单独施放。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="738" y="479" width="408" height="56" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">凛狼迅速高跳至玩家处，并踉跄一下，造成<span color="#99ffff">100%</span><span>伤害。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="738" y="703" width="399" height="56" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">孤狼朝前方猛地喷吐狂风，造成造成<span color="#99ffff">80%</span><span>伤害。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="738" y="927" width="425" height="85" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">凛狼展开半径<span color="#ffdfbf">15m</span><span>的</span><span textDecoration="underline">蕴光领域</span><span>，朝玩家凶猛袭来，并用力切割两次，每次造成</span><span color="#99ffff">70%</span><span>伤害，可连续施放2次。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="738" y="1151" width="425" height="56" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">凛狼展开半径<span color="#ffdfbf">15m</span><span>的</span><span textDecoration="underline">蕴光领域</span><span>，用利爪用力劈开一刀冰刃，造成</span><span color="#99ffff">90%</span><span>伤害。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
